4.  Secrets:
Name	          Commands
List secrets:	  kubectl get secrets â€“all-namespaces

Create a secret: 
> kubectl create secret

List details about secrets:
> kubectl describe secrets

Get secret in yaml:
> kubectl get secret <secret_name> -o yaml

Viewing Kuberentes Secret Values:
> kubectl describe secret mysecondsecret

Delete a secret:
> kubectl delete secret <secret_name>
